React Memo


    - Wouldn't it be nice to utilize the PureComponent concept within functional components?
        - yes..yes it would
        - this is where React Memo comes into play

    
    - React memo is a way to add the pure component functionality to functional components

    How to use it?
        - create a functional component
        - on export of your functional component, use: 
            - export default React.memo(ComponentName)